\fs54 Bars \
\'95 1 oz. unsweetened chocolate \
\'95 1 1/2 sticks melted butter \
\'95 7 eggs, separated \
\'95 1/3 cup sugar \
\'95 1/4 teaspoon cream of tartar \
\'95 1 cups canned chocolate frosting \
\pard\pardeftab720\li80\sl241\ql\qnatural
\cf0 \'95 2 cups whipped cream or whipped topping \
