\fs54 Bars vertically around the cake\'92s sides. \
Spoon the whipped cream into a pastry bag fitted with a large star tip. Cover the cake\'92s top with large piped stars of whipped cream. Sprinkle with cocoa powder. Tie a ribbon around the cake\'92s sides. \
